name: Fitness Jar
summary: The Fitness Jar is a way for me to keep track of the growth and progress of my fitness journey. The goal is to fill the Fitness Jar up to 200 marbles. Once 200 marbles is reached, I would celebrate by getting myself a congratulations gift.
notes: A marble is added into the Fitness Jar for each day that I've worked out.
A marble is added into the Fitness Jar for each week that I have consistently eaten healthily.
As of 3/6/21, I have successfully reached 200 marbles!
